      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Minor suggestion - use <code>URLEncoder.encode(&lt;urlStringToBeEncoded&gt;, StandardCharsets.UTF_8.name())</code>.   Using the static constant <code>UTF_8</code>&#39;s <code>toString()</code> method as the character encoding scheme throws <code>java.nio.charset.IllegalCharsetNameException: java.nio.charset.CharsetICU[UTF-8]</code> as the <code>toString()</code> returns &quot;java.nio.charset.CharsetICU[UTF-8]&quot;. To get the desired &quot;UTF-8&quot; use its <code>name()</code> method instead."
